                            Front. Psychol., 13 September 2021<br>Sec. Health Psychology

                            <br />
                                <span class="volumeInfo"> Volume 12 - 2021 | </span>



                                    <a href="https://doi.org/10.3389/fpsyg.2021.717164">https://doi.org/10.3389/fpsyg.2021.717164</a>
